high_descs: Turn right, move right, take left, turn left towards the side table.
Take the pencil case from the side table.
Turn around, look into the sofa.
Put the pencil case on the sofa.
anns.task_desc: To put the pencil case from side table to sofa.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near side table.
Pick up pencil case from the side table.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the sofa.
Place pencil case on the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Changing pencil case from one place to another.

high_descs:
turn around go straight and turn left to reach the side table 
pick up the pencil case from the side table 
turn right and walk to the sofa
place the pencil case in the sofa
anns.task_desc: place the pencil case in the sofa
